dct_description_sm: Bar scale on map given in "Duytsche mylle."
North oriented toward left of sheet.
Shows fortification, topography, river, vegetation, figures, ships.

Appears in Visscher's Belgium sive Germania Inferior continens provincias singulares septemdecim iuxta artem Geographicam perfectissime descripta, variisque regionum partibus distinctis tabulis aucta per N. J. Piscatorem. Anno 1634.
